<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-82-1095 </DOCNO><TEXT>This report presents an overview of Canada's major oil and gas companies,engaged principally in exploration, development, and marketing; it alsohas interests in gas processing plants, pipelines, oil sands, anthracitemining and overseas operations. Aside from corporate information, currentoperations are described in the following major areas: western Canada,the Hibernia field off the Newfoundland coast, the Beaufort Sea, Egypt,and the Mount Klappan coal field in British Columbia. Statistics (1982-#)on drilling, production, reserves, and land inventory are included. 24figs., 6 tabs.</TEXT></DOC>